Ugandan superstar Vinka and International dance music star Inna have released their new single, 'Bebe', to a global audience. The song is composed of French, Swahili, Luganda and English lyrics. In the video, the two artistes express their style and strong personalities through their outfits, style and the track’s message. Vinka said, “When my team brought me the opportunity to work with the amazingly talented Inna, I was excited beyond words! She was really interested to work Swahili and Luganda lyrics into the song, and the magic between us was instantaneous, she is such an amazing talent.” Inna added, "I love the result, Vinka fits perfectly into the song’s vibe."